Easy to use. The silicone coated barrel ensures a smooth plunger action to easily deliver medications.
Accurate dosing.  The clear barrel of Terumo syringes allows you to quickly recognise air bubbles for more accurate dosing.  With easy to read markings, you can be confident you are delivering the intended dose of medication every time.
Wide range of products
